item.title: CodeCommit
item.description: About CodeCommit is a version control service (Git repository service) that enables the user to personally store & manage Git archives in the AWS cloud. Documentation User Guide CodeCommit is integrated with Jenkins, CodeBuild and other CI tools. Price 5 active users free per month with the Current price Practice Introduction to CodeCommit
